channel.title: I cant log into certain servers because of hamachi
channel.description: well i was trying to log into warscape(pk) but my membership expired on hamachi, and some of the connections got blocked so i couldnt log in. i tried redownloading the prenium trial but it wont work. Can someone help me?

item.title: I cant log into certain servers because of hamachi
item.dc:creator: @Zzz_O_zzZ Zzz O zzZ
item.description:
@Zzz_O_zzZ wrote:

[quote=“slomifier, post:2, topic:80447”]Just dont use hamachi, if you dont undertstand it, use no-ip.

Hamachi dosent even work on my comp; its blocked by all my firewalls and my virus scanner, even if I tell it to allow hamachi.[/quote]

It’s not his server, it’s someone elses.

You don’t need a membership on ham to access ham servers. Just download hamachi, and join existing network.
